&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://amzn.to/4g9m4mN&#34;&gt;NIV Daily Scriptures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Each day features a reading from the Old Testament, New Testament, and Psalm or Proverb.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entries begin with a very short summary of that day’s readings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entries are also undated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-thoughts&#34;&gt;My Thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Convenient to have in one book.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Although covers the Bible in one year, readings always include both the Old and New Testaments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undated entries gives flexibility in start date as well as tempo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Does not follow the church calendar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tim Wildsmith, of &lt;a href=&#34;https://biblereviewblog.com&#34;&gt;BibleReviewBlog.com&lt;/a&gt;, has been going through the Bible and chronicling it on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxYZnUdk-hd1g5_2G56RX9udQIc5KWJwk&#34;&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
